HEADWORD: egocentrism
<hw>egocentrism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the personality trait that
causes one to attempt to get personal recognition for oneself
(especially by unacceptable means).</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> egoism, self-interest, self-concern,
self-centeredness.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Egoical</ent>⟦br⟧
